SuperBackup
===========

Installation
------------
Copy all these files somewhere onto your server.
For example
	/var/www/admin/backup/
	/var/www/admin/backup/README
	/var/www/admin/backup/jobs/config_sample.sh
	/var/www/admin/backup/jobs/file-excludes.txt
	/var/www/admin/backup/jobs/superbackup_names.sh
	/var/www/admin/backup/jobs/superbackup_functions.sh
	/var/www/admin/backup/jobs/superbackup_output.sh

Copy config_sample.sh to config.sh and configure the options for your needs.
Each option is described in the sample document.

Schedule superbackup.sh to run as an automated task
